k/encyklopedi/lång/luis-w-alvarez"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000012192">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://proleksis.lzmk.hr/7217"><i>Proleksis enciklopedija</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Luis_Walter_Alvarez"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a></li>
